productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
My beagle loves to play with it.
This seamless works considerably well. It recklessly improves my basketball by a lot.
My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
